sentences: Andrew "Jr. Boy" Jones (né Andrew Bennie Jones, Jr.; born October 16, 1948) is an American Texas blues guitarist, singer and songwriter, whose recorded work has been released on five albums.
In 1995, he was also part of the ensemble that garnered a Blues Music Award as the 'Band of the Year'.
